{"id":903,"parent_id":890,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":903,"title":"Hosea 13","subtitle":"","short_title":"Hosea","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 13"],[".studySummary",["i","Ephraim’s sins provoke the Lord—There is no Savior beside the Lord—He ransoms from the grave and redeems from death."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.1","order":"02.29.013.60647"},["b","1"],"When Ephraim spake trembling, he exalted himself in Israel; but when he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"offended"],"in Baal, he died."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.2","order":"02.29.013.60648"},["b","2"],"And now they sin more and more, and have made them molten",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"images"],"of their silver,",["i","and"],"idols according to their own understanding, all of it the work of the craftsmen: they say of them, Let the men that sacrifice kiss the calves."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.3","order":"02.29.013.60649"},["b","3"],"Therefore they shall be as the morning cloud, and as the early dew that passeth away, as the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"chaff"],["i","that"],"is driven with the whirlwind out of the floor, and as the smoke out of the chimney."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.4","order":"02.29.013.60650"},["b","4"],"Yet I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God from the land of Egypt, and thou shalt know no",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"god"],"but me: for",["i","there is"],"no",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"saviour"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"beside"],"me."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.5","order":"02.29.013.60651"},["b","5"],"¶I did",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"know"],"thee in the wilderness, in the land of great",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"drought"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.6","order":"02.29.013.60652"},["b","6"],"According to their pasture, so were they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"filled"],"; they were filled, and their heart was exalted; therefore have they",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"forgotten"],"me."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.7","order":"02.29.013.60653"},["b","7"],"Therefore I will be unto them as a lion: as a leopard by the way will I observe",["i","them:"]],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.8","order":"02.29.013.60654"},["b","8"],"I will meet them as a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"bear"],["i","that is"],"bereaved",["i","of her whelps,"],"and will rend the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"caul"],"of their heart, and there will I devour them like a lion: the wild beast shall tear them."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.9","order":"02.29.013.60655"},["b","9"],"¶O Israel, thou hast",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"destroyed"],"thyself; but in me",["i","is"],"thine",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"help"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.10","order":"02.29.013.60656"},["b","10"],"I will be thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"king"],": where",["i","is any other"],"that may save thee in all thy cities? and thy judges of whom thou saidst, Give me a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"king"],"and princes?"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.11","order":"02.29.013.60657"},["b","11"],"I gave thee a king in mine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"anger"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"took"],["i","him"],"away in my wrath."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.12","order":"02.29.013.60658"},["b","12"],"The iniquity of Ephraim",["i","is"],"bound up; his sin",["i","is"],"hid."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.13","order":"02.29.013.60659"},["b","13"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"sorrows"],"of a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"travailing"],"woman shall come upon him: he",["i","is"],"an unwise son; for he should not stay long in",["i","the place of"],"the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"breaking"],"forth of children."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.14","order":"02.29.013.60660"},["b","14"],"I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"ransom"],"them from the power of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"grave"],"; I will",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"redeem"],"them from death: O",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_14d"},"death"],", I will be thy",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_14e"},"plagues"],"; O grave, I will be thy destruction:",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_14f"},"repentance"],"shall be hid from mine eyes."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.15","order":"02.29.013.60661"},["b","15"],"¶Though he be fruitful among",["i","his"],"brethren, an east",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"wind"],"shall come, the wind of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall come up from the wilderness, and his spring shall become dry, and his fountain shall be dried up: he shall spoil the treasure of all pleasant vessels."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.16","order":"02.29.013.60662"},["b","16"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"Samaria"],"shall become desolate; for she hath rebelled against her God: they shall fall by the sword: their infants shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"dashed"],"in pieces, and their women with child shall be ripped up."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.1a","order":"02.29.013.60663"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/11.2"},"Hosea 11:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.2a","order":"02.29.013.60665"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.15"},"Deut. 27:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.3a","order":"02.29.013.60667"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/1.4"},"Ps. 1:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/26.18"},"2 Ne. 26:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/5.16.16-18"},"Morm. 5:16 (16–18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.4a","order":"02.29.013.60669"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/12.35"},"Mosiah 12:35"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.4b","order":"02.29.013.60671"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.12"},"Acts 4:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/25.20"},"2 Ne. 25:20"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-jehovah"},"TG Jesus Christ, Jehovah"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-redeemer"},"Jesus Christ, Redeemer"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.4c","order":"02.29.013.60673"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/43.11"},"Isa. 43:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.1"},"D&C 76:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.5a","order":"02.29.013.60675"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/2.7"},"Deut. 2:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.5b","order":"02.29.013.60677"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/drought"},"TG Drought"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.6a","order":"02.29.013.60679"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.16.12,16"},"Deut. 8:16 (12, 16)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.28.26-29"},"1 Ne. 17:28 (26–29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.6b","order":"02.29.013.60681"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-individuals"},"TG Apostasy of Individuals"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.8a","order":"02.29.013.60683"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/17.12"},"Prov. 17:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.8b","order":"02.29.013.60685"},["b","8b"],["span.small","IE"],"cha